00:14:46.080 --> 00:14:48.390
Nang walang inaasahan, ang mga bono ay magtatagal.

00:14:49.150 --> 00:14:50.700
Anong klaseng pangangatwiran yan?

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:52.960
